name: @ionic-native/fcm
readme: Improve this doc # FCM ``` $ ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-fcm-with-dependecy-updated $ npm install --save @ionic-native/fcm ``` ## [Usage Documentation](https://ionicframework.com/docs/native/fcm/) Plugin Repo: [https://github.com/andrehtissot/cordova-plugin-fcm-with-dependecy-updated](https://github.com/andrehtissot/cordova-plugin-fcm-with-dependecy-updated) Provides basic functionality for Firebase Cloud Messaging ## Supported platforms - Android - iOS
